import { Component } from '@angular/core'; import { MatDialog } from '@angular/material/dialog'; import { DailogLoginComponent } from '../dailog-login/dailog-login.component'; import { DailogSignupComponent } from '../dailog-signup/dailog-signup.component'; import { MyserviceService } from '../myservice.service'; @Component({ selector: 'app-biryani-bay', templateUrl: './biryani-bay.component.html', styleUrls: ['./biryani-bay.component.css'] }) export class BiryaniBayComponent { login!:boolean user: any; userget: any; clicked: boolean = false dishes:any[]=[] constructor(public dialog: MatDialog, private service: MyserviceService) { } ngOnInit(): void { this.service.check() this.service.datachangeobservable.subscribe((d) => (this.login = d)); this.user = localStorage.getItem('Name') const user1 = this.user.replaceAll('"', ' ') this.userget = user1 } openDialog() { this.dialog.open(DailogLoginComponent); } opensignupDialog() { this.dialog.open(DailogSignupComponent); } Recommended: any = [ { id: 1, dish: "Chicken Cheese Grilled Sandwich", price: 130, }, { id: 2, dish: "Lassi Sweet", price: 130 }, { id: 3, dish: "Fruit Salad with Ice Cream", price: 130 }, { id: 4, dish: "Caramel Custard", price: 130 }, { id: 5, dish: "Fresh Lime Soda", price: 130 }, { id: 6, dish: "Lassi Salty", price: 130 }, { id: 7, dish: "Lassi Sweet", price: 130 }, { id: 8, dish: "Mountain Dew", price: 130 }, { id: 9, dish: "Pepsi", price: 130 }, ] add_to_cart(item: any) { this.clicked = true setTimeout(() => { this.clicked=false }, 1000); this.dishes.push(item) localStorage.setItem('Dishes', JSON.stringify(this.dishes)); console.log(localStorage.getItem('Dishes')) } logout() { localStorage.removeItem("pass") localStorage.removeItem("loginId") local } }
